snippet.title: Arcane Saga Online Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Beta starts May 7th! Sign up here: http://as.netmarble.com/

Heroes rally, a world is reborn. Arcane Saga Online thrusts players into the world of Prius, where they will encounter deadly creatures, befriend the mysterious Anima and start their own divine journey to save the world. Sign up for Beta beginning on May 7th 2013! 

Like and Follow us!
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ArcaneSaga
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ArcaneSaga
